    <body>
        <p>It is also possible to install all of the Pulse components on a single server. This means the Pulse web server and database server are running on a single system. Although this is a simple way to deploy Pulse, most organizations choose to install Pulse in a distributed environment because it offers greater scalability and performance.</p>
